755
00:31:17,800 --> 00:31:18,680
I need to thank her.

756
00:31:19,300 --> 00:31:20,140
Okay.

757
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:21,720
I'll get you some water.

758
00:31:26,430 --> 00:31:27,300
